## ⌨️ Global Hardware Mapping Code Constants

| Constant | Hardware Resource |
| :--- | :--- |
| `pyforge.KEY_W` / `KEY_UP` | Keyboard W Key / Up Arrow Movement |
| `pyforge.KEY_A` / `KEY_LEFT` | Keyboard A Key / Left Arrow Movement |
| `pyforge.KEY_S` / `KEY_DOWN` | Keyboard S Key / Down Arrow Movement |
| `pyforge.KEY_D` / `KEY_RIGHT` | Keyboard D Key / Right Arrow Movement |
| `pyforge.KEY_SPACE` | Keyboard Spacebar Trigger |
| `pyforge.MOUSE_LEFT` | Primary Mouse Button Click |

